  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>Dear Aisling,
 Were you not the one that discovered the Emerald Knight's insignia? That must mean you are a worthy soul. It seems that I have misplaced my lute. Without this lute, I am unable to fulfill my duty as a bard! I do not recall where I lost it, however I was meeting with Eeva the last time I had it. Perhaps you should begin your search there... but I pray you do hurry, I feel incomplete without it!

- Mioas
Traveling Bard of Suomi

Legend marks will be given to the first ten aislings to find Mioas' Lute. Prizes will be awarded to random participants who complete this event.

